cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.DL 

The paper deals with classification problems in online social networks, specifically focusing on the detection of global and local nodes. This falls under the sub-category of social and information networks (cs.SI) as well as social computing (cs.SOC). The use of AI and prediction algorithms also suggests a connection to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL). Finally, the paper also involves information retrieval (cs.IR) in terms of analyzing and processing data from Facebook public pages.
